      <title>交易员注意到央行对大胆降息押注的抵制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/markets-heed-central-bank-pushback-against-aggressive-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大债券市场的交易员正在关注央行的警告，并减少对今年大幅降息的押注。]]></description>
