    <item>
      <title>美国提出打击高额透支费用的规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/us-proposes-new-rule-to-end-high-overdraft-fees-in-crack-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府公布了一项期待已久的法规，该法规可能会将最大银行的透支费收入每年削减多达 35 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/us-proposes-new-rule-to-end-high-overdraft-fees-in-crack-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在可靠数据公布后，华尔街调整了对美联储的押注：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/stocks-bonds-fall-as-traders-tweak-rate-cut-hopes-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于押注美联储不会急于降息，因为经济显示出强劲的迹象，债券收益率攀升，股市与风险资产一起下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/stocks-bonds-fall-as-traders-tweak-rate-cut-hopes-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 22:45:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
